    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Humbug Tales: Keeper of the Swarm</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为蚁后陛下收集种子币、附近的自然资源以及食物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >繁育一个分工明确、各司其职的强大蚁群。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调度你的蚂蚁控制障碍物、组成蚁桥、跟踪信息素的痕迹。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指挥虫子蜂拥群攻，更要借势借物，临机应变，一举消灭敌人。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277190/extras/115e0ce4a3c6df222a9813d751ad532d.avif?t=1768770903\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277190/extras_big/115e0ce4a3c6df222a9813d751ad532d.avif?t=1768770903 width=800 height=302 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>穿越荷塘，</strong>追寻失踪已久的孩子。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中，你将遇见形形色色的虫子和“虫人”朋友，有古怪的蜘蛛虫倌，也有居无定所，但能在夜里闪闪发光的沙漠隐游郎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但要小心，上方的天空是昆虫世界里可怕的蜂后达格玛的家园。在她的眈眈虎视下，你和你的蚁群将面临邪恶的强盗蚂蚁、僵尸真菌以及狂热的黄蜂虫人。   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277190/extras/e60b2a8364bfc46e28472a20669c455d.avif?t=1768770903\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277190/extras_big/e60b2a8364bfc46e28472a20669c455d.avif?t=1768770903 width=800 height=302 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>指挥你的小虫子，</strong>在水清木秀的湿地中一路穿行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组成蚁桥，跨越水沟。使用集体的力量，操控环境，发现可供探索的新区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想要扩大蚁群规模，你必须奉养蚁后！散布信息素痕迹，指向新的食物资源，哺育勤劳的工蚁、强大的兵蚁、长翅膀的飞蚁和肥胀的贮蜜蚁来扩大你的蚁群。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277190/extras/5f35d2afbcd3ad907673d55d3987ea57.avif?t=1768770903\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277190/extras_big/5f35d2afbcd3ad907673d55d3987ea57.avif?t=1768770903 width=800 height=302 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>集结虫群，</strong>对抗昆虫王国的凶猛大虫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要打败凶猛的天敌和敌对虫人，你需要智慧、勇气以及——蛛丝武器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有同心协力，你和你的六脚朋友才能取得胜利。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>试玩版现已孵化！</strong>即刻添加愿望单，感受不一样的异虫与妙境体验！</i></h2>",
